room_title: Escape room "Heist" by Escape This in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_address: 4372 Spring Valley Rd Farmers Branch, TX 75244
room_description: Thomas Gardner is the popular in-house counsel for ISG Corp: his employees love him, his shareholders love him, and the media loves him. But when millions suddenly goes missing, one suspicious shareholder thinks the in-house counsel is actually embezzling funds. Mr. Gardner has hired you to track down the funds and clear his name, but is there more to this white collar crime than first meets the eye?
